T1  - A Re-Examination of the Market Reaction to Failed Mergers
AU  - DAVIDSON III, WALLACE N.
AU  - DUTIA, DIPA
AU  - CHENG, LOUIS
Y1  - 1989/09/01
PY  - 1989
DA  - 1989/09/01
